OL,3,CHunt for convict who failed to return
OL,4,Cto open prison
OL,6,FPolice are looking for a convict who
OL,7,Ffailed to return to open prison.
OL,9,FEdwin Newman, who is serving a
OL,10,Fsentence for threats to kill and false
OL,11,Fimprisonment, left the Sudbury Prison
OL,12,Fin Derbyshire at 11.40am on Thursday.
OL,14,FHe had been let out for a period of
OL,15,Fday release, but failed to return
OL,16,Flater that day.
OL,18,FThe 45-year-old is described as being
OL,19,Fwhite with a bald head and stubble.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/2
