PN,34402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F344A1784560725
OL,3,CHunt for convict who failed to return
OL,4,Cto open prison
OL,6,FHe was last seen wearing grey jogging
OL,7,Fbottoms, a white Ben Sherman t-shirt,
OL,8,Fgrey Nike jumper and blue Nike
OL,9,Ftrainers.
OL,11,FNewman has links to Weymouth and
OL,12,FManchester.
OL,14,FAnyone who sees him is asked not to
OL,15,Fapproach him and to report the
OL,16,Fsighting to Derbyshire Constabulary.
